{"word":"G2782 - κήρυγμα - kḗrygma - kay'-roog-mah - Preaching","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κήρυγμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kḗrygma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kay'-roog-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Preaching"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பிரசங்கம் - பால்வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"that which is promulgated by a herald or public crier, a pro clamation by herald"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2784 - κηρύσσω - kērýssō - kay-roos'-so/2784\">G2784</a>; a <i>proclamation</i> (especially of the gospel; by implication the <i>gospel</i> itself): - preaching."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2782 - κήρυγμα - kḗrygma - kay'-roog-mah/2782\">G2782</a>, <a href=\"#/G2783 - κῆρυξ - kēryx - kay'-roox/2783\">G2783</a>, <a href=\"#/G2784 - κηρύσσω - kērýssō - kay-roos'-so/2784\">G2784</a>, <a href=\"#/G4296 - προκηρύσσω - prokērýssō - prok-ay-rooce'-so/4296\">G4296</a>"}]}